&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or equivalent work experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of work experience in DevOps, Release Engineering, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience deploying and managing Docker containers across Kubernetes or similar container orchestration systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Terraform, Ansible, or Helm.&lt;/li&gt;
