&lt;li&gt;Research and productize (Prototyping to Production) the latest computer vision and deep learning papers (CVPR, ICCV, IROS, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advance multi-sensor fusion (LiDAR-LiDAR, LiDAR-Camera) algorithms and resolve complex edge cases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead code reviews and design reviews, and provide technical mentoring for junior engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze system performance bottlenecks and establish optimization strategies utilizing various techniques including hardware acceleration (e.g., CUDA, TensorRT).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product teams and other departments to define technical requirements and support roadmap establishment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
