&lt;p&gt;■&amp;nbsp; Keep Growing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;■&amp;nbsp; Respect Diversity&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mission of the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone to help build Seoul Robotics&#39; path into the capital markets. We&#39;re preparing for a KOSDAQ technology-track IPO, and we need someone to own the full capital markets workstream — IPO execution, disclosure &amp;amp; governance, and IR. Join us at the Associate level and build your own track, or come in as a Senior to drive the full cycle. Either way, you&#39;ll work directly with our lead underwriter, the Korea Exchange (KRX), external counsel, and global investors — sitting at the center of the company&#39;s most important strategic conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need to walk in with every skill already mastered. What we need is someone who can take a fuzzy problem, define it, learn what&#39;s missing, and see it through. Ownership and learning agility are what we hire for — everything else, we&#39;ll build together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IPO Execution (45%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the KOSDAQ technology-track listing — work with the lead underwriter and manage KRX review (pre-consultation, expert panel, on-site due diligence); prepare and own the listing application and supporting documents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the technical evaluation process with external assessment agencies (initial evaluation and re-evaluation).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pre-IPO investment management — review investment agreements, amendment letters, and governance clauses (drag/tag-along) in coordination with external counsel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Investor Relations (30%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain IR Decks in both Korean and English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead overseas investor NDRs and draft term sheets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run quarterly investor updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with BD on revenue projections, valuation, and pricing policy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design revenue recognition policy and OPEX (recurring revenue) structure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
